snippet.title: SNES Longplay [197] Psycho Dream
snippet.description:

Played by Valis77

This game is made by the company that made the Valis series.  Two courageous demon hunters (Ryo and Maria) who decide to go on a mystical journey to free the world of living people from the demons. -
